# Planning Granularity

- Keep high-level stream intent in `docs/ROADMAP/subplans/`.
- Keep volatile day-to-day details in `docs/EXECUTION/`.
- Maintain detailed plans for current and next phase; keep later phases concise.
- Phase transitions should update roadmap status, execution checklist, and any resulting decisions.
- For planning updates, milestone edits, or phase-transition tasks, run `.cursor/skills/docs-phase-planning-maintainer/SKILL.md`.
- If the task is an implementation request that may affect planning docs, run `.cursor/skills/docs-implementation-gate/SKILL.md` and include a planning pass.
